de.tub.data.dao
Interface IFrameworkClusterDAO<E>

All Superinterfaces:
IDao
All Known Implementing Classes:
Neo4JFrameworkClusterDAO
public interface IFrameworkClusterDAO<E>
extends IDao

This interface provides methods to access Framework cluster. The IFrameworkClusterDAO is part of the Data Access Object design pattern.

Author:
Sebastian Oelke
